{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Enerdusk&quot;</strong> is a roguelike deck-building game where you create strategies centered around units while utilizing cards. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cards empower your units, and in turn, the enhanced units strengthen your deck and tip the battle in your favor. Activate unit skills with the effects of cards and items to turn the tide of battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/SkillAct.gif?t=1736862603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout the game, you can recruit various companions (units), and the player can form a team of up to four units to take into battle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each companion is powered by cards and uses unique skills. Find victory through clever combinations of cards and units.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/backPack.gif?t=1736862603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even during battles, you can add new cards to your deck by using cards from your backpack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Some unit skills allow you to remove unnecessary cards, enabling quick deck adjustments mid-combat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play higher-quality hands and unleash powerful skills against your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/enemy.gif?t=1736862603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies use always-visible enemy cards to deal damage to your units. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Since enemy cards are constantly revealed, it\u2019s up to you to decide whether to attack, defend, or strengthen your deck. Your choices and decisions will determine the flow of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/shop.jpg?t=1736862603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Through events, companions can acquire and equip various items. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the optimal combinations between your units and your deck to build the ultimate party!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3302460?t=1736862603","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3302460?t=1736862603","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/ac9cfc1147df98f93b452cac68c4b0eccd31ac48/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736862603","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/ac9cfc1147df98f93b452cac68c4b0eccd31ac48/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736862603","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Enerdusk&quot;</strong> is a roguelike deck-building game where you create strategies centered around units while utilizing cards. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cards empower your units, and in turn, the enhanced units strengthen your deck and tip the battle in your favor. Activate unit skills with the effects of cards and items to turn the tide of battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/SkillAct.gif?t=1736862603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout the game, you can recruit various companions (units), and the player can form a team 